<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Welcome to Our Platform</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Cambria sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #007bff;
      }
      p {
        color: #333;
      }
      ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
      }
      li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      span {
        color: dodgerblue;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to Our Platform!</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome to our platform! We're thrilled to have you on board. To ensure a
      positive experience for everyone, we kindly request that you familiarize
      yourself with our rules of engagement. These guidelines are designed to
      create a respectful and inclusive environment for all users. By following
      these rules, you contribute to the vibrant community we're building
      together. Thank you for your cooperation, and we look forward to your
      active participation!
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <span>Respect Others:</span> Treat fellow users with kindness and
        respect. Avoid any form of harassment, discrimination, or offensive
        language. Healthy and constructive discussions are encouraged.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span>Keep it Civil:</span> Disagreements are natural, but express your
        opinions and disagreements in a civil manner. Personal attacks or
        hostility will not be tolerated.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span>Stay on Topic:</span> Contribute relevant content to discussions
        and posts. Straying off-topic can make it difficult for others to find
        valuable information.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span> Protect Privacy:</span> Respect the privacy of others. Do not
        share personal information, such as addresses or contact details,
        without permission.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span>Report Issues: </span>If you encounter behavior that violates our
        guidelines, report it to our moderation team. Your vigilance helps
        maintain a safe and enjoyable platform for all.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact us at
      support@ourplatform.com.
    </p>

    <p>Here is your One-Time Password (OTP):</p>
    <ul>
      <li style="color: grey; font-weight: 700; font-size: 40px"><%= otp %></li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      To get continue with your registration process, kindly click this link:
    </p>
    <p><a href="<%= url %>"><%= url %></a></p>

    <p>Enjoy your experience on our platform!</p>
  </body>
</html>
